{"tid":220750,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"每日只係返工放工...想搵樣目標/興趣比自己去做...","createTime":"2017-04-28T07:49:21.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-28T18:29:16.000Z","uid":32248,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"1948f870e32ce010ec17f9aca84d431447f889b1","tid":220750,"uid":32248,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-28T07:49:21.000Z","msg":"有無巴打同我一樣....<br />\n三十歲人, 每日都淨係返工等放工  (我仲要係返shift既工, 一星期返足6日)<br />\n放工 食飯 打機<br />\n生活平淡<br />\n<br />\n其實一直好想搵樣目標/興趣<br />\n其中最大興趣想學跆拳道<br />\n由細到大都想...細個屋企人又唔比玩武術<br />\n但係30歲人先黎開始  會唔會好ON9<br />\n只係想當係做下運動, 又或者考個黑帶當係自己既一個目標<br />\n<br />\n另外又想學好英文...<br />\n一直都好屎...<br />\n去旅行  完整一句英文都唔係好講到<br />\n只係一直靠讀生字<br />\n<br />\n定係.....長期係屋企鳩hea  返到公司鳩做<br />\n咁就一世算<br />\n有無巴打可以比d 動力我  或者入黎吹下水 <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile_big.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b94dd9c608d3ba2f00acff6b97f9cf7a3e490ab8","tid":220750,"uid":100094,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-28T07:55:11.000Z","msg":"自學樂器<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n想做就去做 想學咩就去學<br />\n無謂後悔<br />\n岩唔岩先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8b27caeb15ae87ae328fa95a4c7cbbceba6671ba","tid":220750,"uid":32248,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-28T07:59:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>自學樂器<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n想做就去做 想學咩就去學<br />\n無謂後悔<br />\n岩唔岩先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n巴打你有自學樂器? <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"516e3121c722dc25d2001fee3ffe33ba29bb09d9","tid":220750,"uid":38461,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-28T08:00:32.000Z","msg":"俾左錢就會去嫁啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"80afd21e28707237d7bdd5180da6dc56f98ab6f3","tid":220750,"uid":46933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-28T08:01:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>俾左錢就會去嫁啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n依樣真<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8fd12a15457bd602bf561154932ba28c4777e8cd","tid":220750,"uid":100094,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-28T08:05:38.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>自學樂器<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n想做就去做 想學咩就去學<br />\n無謂後悔<br />\n岩唔岩先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n巴打你有自學樂器? <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n讀緊書 以前都係嗰d一有時間就玩電腦嘅人 不過人大咗 諗多咗 發覺咁樣好on9 好浪費時間 所以決定搵樣樂器自學自娛 迫自己keep住學新鮮而又有興趣嘅野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"73f49396a32994b8c2549e800e2ab6f9269ee63f","tid":220750,"uid":40536,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-28T08:06:05.000Z","msg":"樓主加油 我都無目標 做人唔知做緊咩"},{"pid":"d74cd5f3b963702d4c81761a303251ba4e2341de","tid":220750,"uid":32248,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-28T08:06:56.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>自學樂器<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n想做就去做 想學咩就去學<br />\n無謂後悔<br />\n岩唔岩先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n巴打你有自學樂器? <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n讀緊書 以前都係嗰d一有時間就玩電腦嘅人 不過人大咗 諗多咗 發覺咁樣好on9 好浪費時間 所以決定搵樣樂器自學自娛 迫自己keep住學新鮮而又有興趣嘅野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n當中會唔會有段時間想放棄學緊既野?"},{"pid":"70bd007d3a202c7a9af86003e61be2b355fdda75","tid":220750,"uid":32248,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-28T08:07:33.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>樓主加油 我都無目標 做人唔知做緊咩</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n一齊加油啦...<br />\n我好三心兩意<br />\n好多野都想學<br />\n但又未有動力去踏出第一步 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f22978239d7bcdc21709022bd8a853b2bd7dc6a7","tid":220750,"uid":100094,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-28T08:11:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>自學樂器<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n想做就去做 想學咩就去學<br />\n無謂後悔<br />\n岩唔岩先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n巴打你有自學樂器? <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n讀緊書 以前都係嗰d一有時間就玩電腦嘅人 不過人大咗 諗多咗 發覺咁樣好on9 好浪費時間 所以決定搵樣樂器自學自娛 迫自己keep住學新鮮而又有興趣嘅野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n當中會唔會有段時間想放棄學緊既野?</blockquote><br />\n梗會有試過 但當你初有所成或者諗起之前嘅自己幾咁頹嘅時候 你就唔會放棄<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8f8a030f29d1c4e18c59b8cda4c0e39bec58dbc2","tid":220750,"uid":9924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-28T08:13:02.000Z","msg":"返shift其實真係無乜時間去做其他要跟時間表既野<br />\n尤其係上堂"},{"pid":"bee6d432a51d45ae999b36bdbfe7104df40dfd9f","tid":220750,"uid":32248,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-28T08:29:37.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>返shift其實真係無乜時間去做其他要跟時間表既野<br />\n尤其係上堂</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n巴打都係返SHIFT 工?"},{"pid":"501fff90c354cc7438b691ae93c8bf8cdeae30f0","tid":220750,"uid":9924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-28T08:31:07.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>返shift其實真係無乜時間去做其他要跟時間表既野<br />\n尤其係上堂</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n巴打都係返SHIFT 工?</blockquote><br />\n垃圾shift工<br />\n返六日<br />\n唔係特別辛苦<br />\n但係有野想學又就唔到時間<br />\n攞一年經驗就走諗住"},{"pid":"dc6aac4cb8a54638de9f83c3f8b4e3b9d9d740cb","tid":220750,"uid":32248,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-28T08:33:40.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>返shift其實真係無乜時間去做其他要跟時間表既野<br />\n尤其係上堂</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n巴打都係返SHIFT 工?</blockquote><br />\n垃圾shift工<br />\n返六日<br />\n唔係特別辛苦<br />\n但係有野想學又就唔到時間<br />\n攞一年經驗就走諗住</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我都係返足6日...<br />\n你講得啱...返SHIFT 又返6日, 最難就係就時間去上堂...<br />\n唉  可惜  我學歷唔高, 宜家呢份工已經對我黎講算係最好....<br />\n亦因為咁....拎唔起動力去學其他野 <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6bee542d253456aefdf991b3bf71a3de971e31f3","tid":220750,"uid":9924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-28T08:37:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>返shift其實真係無乜時間去做其他要跟時間表既野<br />\n尤其係上堂</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n巴打都係返SHIFT 工?</blockquote><br />\n垃圾shift工<br />\n返六日<br />\n唔係特別辛苦<br />\n但係有野想學又就唔到時間<br />\n攞一年經驗就走諗住</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我都係返足6日...<br />\n你講得啱...返SHIFT 又返6日, 最難就係就時間去上堂...<br />\n唉  可惜  我學歷唔高, 宜家呢份工已經對我黎講算係最好....<br />\n亦因為咁....拎唔起動力去學其他野 <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n儲舊錢 quit左佢學下想學既野<br />\n做下想做既野<br />\n咁岩有專業證書就仲好<br />\n我唔太信呢一代一份工打一世<br />\n始終唔同左時代"},{"pid":"b7852a844b4b5654169f046f10262594660faebf","tid":220750,"uid":32248,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-28T10:07:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>返shift其實真係無乜時間去做其他要跟時間表既野<br />\n尤其係上堂</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n巴打都係返SHIFT 工?</blockquote><br />\n垃圾shift工<br />\n返六日<br />\n唔係特別辛苦<br />\n但係有野想學又就唔到時間<br />\n攞一年經驗就走諗住</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我都係返足6日...<br />\n你講得啱...返SHIFT 又返6日, 最難就係就時間去上堂...<br />\n唉  可惜  我學歷唔高, 宜家呢份工已經對我黎講算係最好....<br />\n亦因為咁....拎唔起動力去學其他野 <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n儲舊錢 quit左佢學下想學既野<br />\n做下想做既野<br />\n咁岩有專業證書就仲好<br />\n我唔太信呢一代一份工打一世<br />\n始終唔同左時代</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n結左婚, 又孭緊層樓, 遲下又要生小朋友<br />\n唔可以話quit 就quit <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n這就是hk"},{"pid":"d61edc97d960af82b78e2937d7855198175915a3","tid":220750,"uid":45545,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-28T10:23:37.000Z","msg":"我都係咁 比點目標自己喇 加油😃"},{"pid":"faaec4aa09122bd6eb6913792023dd1bbfbbe4df","tid":220750,"uid":188,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-28T10:25:42.000Z","msg":"你覺得捕住個po<br />\n用時間諗一萬個藉口拒絕實行第一步<br />\n係目前最佳方法？"},{"pid":"681dbd0e02e41badf6fe975515f6380f5b66b3ef","tid":220750,"uid":9924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-28T10:28:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>返shift其實真係無乜時間去做其他要跟時間表既野<br />\n尤其係上堂</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n巴打都係返SHIFT 工?</blockquote><br />\n垃圾shift工<br />\n返六日<br />\n唔係特別辛苦<br />\n但係有野想學又就唔到時間<br />\n攞一年經驗就走諗住</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我都係返足6日...<br />\n你講得啱...返SHIFT 又返6日, 最難就係就時間去上堂...<br />\n唉  可惜  我學歷唔高, 宜家呢份工已經對我黎講算係最好....<br />\n亦因為咁....拎唔起動力去學其他野 <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n儲舊錢 quit左佢學下想學既野<br />\n做下想做既野<br />\n咁岩有專業證書就仲好<br />\n我唔太信呢一代一份工打一世<br />\n始終唔同左時代</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n結左婚, 又孭緊層樓, 遲下又要生小朋友<br />\n唔可以話quit 就quit <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n這就是hk</blockquote><br />\n路你人行出黎既<br />\n最難捱唔係無錢<br />\n無人支持先辛苦"},{"pid":"8a32e7ddf50f4a2973360f05f5078d63175d68a7","tid":220750,"uid":75704,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-28T10:29:07.000Z","msg":"shift係咩意思 ？ sales行業？"},{"pid":"b5272c482aa2a17f070c31cc92bd657f18b28780","tid":220750,"uid":75704,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-28T10:29:37.000Z","msg":"我都一樣冇目標呀 每日只係番工放工<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"06c7cb086089e3c4e271950293f56c79e4c8d443","tid":220750,"uid":9924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-28T10:31:45.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>shift係咩意思 ？ sales行業？</blockquote><br />\n輪更制"},{"pid":"933bc9093bece7f3ca933b360ef70743a898e969","tid":220750,"uid":75704,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-28T12:26:27.000Z","msg":"如果真係要目標 我想識留個女友<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"811818437bea33265b23244ce86ef8b6f860a50c","tid":220750,"uid":75704,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-28T12:26:58.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>如果真係要目標 我想識<span style=\"color: red;\">番</span>個女友<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>"},{"pid":"f87d68efcf6cbdafdbcc4a4fce662e15e2856680","tid":220750,"uid":32248,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-28T13:36:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>如果真係要目標 我想識<span style=\"color: red;\">番</span>個女友<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n實有既<br />\n遲早問題 <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}